{
  "stem": "25591.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I sensed that this is a historic day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So for the first time in my life, I took out my little pouch and took the few pennies that I had and bought that newspaper and, and took it home, because I knew I was bringing home an important piece of news.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were not kosher.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We observed the high holidays.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was bar mitzvahed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We celebrated Hanukkah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We fasted on Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I, I felt very Jewish in a, in a cultural and political sense.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- Jews come in many sizes and shapes, and, and there was a lot of discussion about converting and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I never entertained that for a moment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, I was very proud to be a Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean why the family did not leave?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, in retrospect not leaving appears like an idiotic decision.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And since in '38, '39 I was 10, 11 years old, I, I have difficulty putting myself in the boots of, of my elders.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I believe that the main reason was that the enormity of the Holocaust that was to follow could not be conceived.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, we, we, we-- you know, we listened to the BBC and we listened to, to Western broadcast.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we understood that a war is coming and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the expectation was that we would survive the war, that Hungary, under Admiral Horthy, was an ally of Germany, and it will be difficult for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it, it never crossed anyone's mind in our family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Obviously, it was a fatal flaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Jews would be exterminated.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
